    "description": "这是一款基于现实题材的中国式情商生存，“魂系”生存游戏。从14亿人中选出真正能带领国足夺得世界杯的天赋型教练。<br>需要平衡好足协、球员、球迷、财政，同时也要融合了《paper，please》玩法，筛选合适的球员进入球队，避免选错离奇下课。<br>游戏包含了无数种中国国足主教练的下课结局，大量“真实”的演出漫画，能够让你感受到中国足球残酷的生存环境，本作是真魂系难度，小白玩家劝退。<br>如果您坚持不信邪，躲避无数下课陷阱，坚持要带领国足拿到世界杯，那也许您就是我们一直在寻找的、永不下课的天才教练！<br><br>qq群：163984947<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/a8d2e6f92aa4dd155f1ff139b3f0b668.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/323778c09b99d95e5722fdc4639502b1.avif?t=1722250020\" width=570 height=73 /></span><br><br>在【教练，please】游戏中，各种“人才”纷纷希望加入国足。你需要仔细甄别他们的言辞，决定是否让他们加入球队。一旦决策失误，就可能带来严重的后果！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/ad964d83f8766024ad8e888d1f4b3af1.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=357 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/51c816d836e4075e6463ffd59155faef.avif?t=1722250020\" width=570 height=73 /></span><br><br>成为教练远不止于执教球队，球员受伤时你需要运用针灸疗法，上级不满时你还得提供推拿足疗服务。无数你意想不到的挑战正等着你。然而，这一切都是赢取世界杯的必经之路！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/31701ad25378ca9c9ff9687aa564a7c2.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=294 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/ea649081ae71ceba4051d28ab57f5ea0.avif?t=1722250020\" width=570 height=73 /></span><br><br>没点儿公关能力，根本做不好国足主教练，这个世界对男足恶意很大，你需要再多忍一下！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/19ffd70bac828525b066a601bc191833.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=326 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/51848406a1e3e4e1cb802664c634b5d8.avif?t=1722250020\" width=570 height=73 /></span><br><br>虽然看到其他玩家夺取世界杯让人羡慕，但他们解锁的一些奇葩下课结局可能更让人揪心！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/9ef19840f28db1182b98d29e47b2a5d2.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=410 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/1a1d8ffc248bae56208dfc0813a51005.avif?t=1722250020\" width=570 height=73 /></span><br><br>每场比赛都有解说演出，无需体育VIP，无需广告90秒，点开即看！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/6f191f4168957d10c49a27771506c316.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=331 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021330/extras/c7964c7a859073429255737b39becc1b.avif?t=1722250020\" width=600 height=104 /></span>",
